ert]]\n|-\n|align=center|17\n|align=right|26 Apr 2004\n|[[Shell Houston Open]] <small>(2)</small>\n|\u221211 (74-66-69-68=277)\n|2 strokes\n|{{flagicon|USA}} [[Scott Hoch]]\n|-\n|align=center|18\n|align=right|3 May 2004\n|[[HP Classic of New Orleans]]\n|\u221222 (70-65-68-63=266)\n|1 stroke\n|{{flagicon|USA}} [[Phil Mickelson]], {{flagicon|USA}} [[Joe Ogilvie]]\n|-\n|align=center|19\n|align=right|1 Aug 2004\n|[[Buick Open]] <small>(2)</small>\n|\u221223 (63-70-65-67=265)\n|1 stroke\n|{{flagicon|USA}} [[John Daly (golfer)|John Daly]]\n|- style=\"background:#e5d1cb;\"\n|align=center|20\n|align=right|15 Aug 2004\n|'''[[2004 PGA Championship|PGA Championship]]''' <small>(2)</small>\n|\u22128 (67-68-69-76=280)\n|Playoff\n|{{flagicon|USA}} [[Chris DiMarco]], {{flagicon|USA}} [[Justin Leonard]]\n|-\n|align=center|21\n|align=right|6 Sep 2004\n|[[Deutsche Bank Championship]]\n|\u221216 (68-63-68-69=268)\n|3 strokes\n|{{flagicon|AUS}} [[Adam Scott (golfer)|Adam Scott]], {{flagicon|USA}} [[Tiger Woods]]\n|-\n|align=center|22\n|align=right|12 Sep 2004\n|[[Bell Canadian Open]]\n|\u22129 (68-66-72-69=275)\n|Playoff\n|{{flagicon|CAN}} [[Mike Weir]]\n|-\n|align=center|23\n|align=right|26 Sep 2004\n|[[84 Lumber Classic]]\n|\u221215 (64-68-72-69=273)\n|1 stroke\n|{{flagicon|USA}} [[Stewart Cink]]\n|-\n|align=center|24\n|align=right|31 Oct 2004\n|[[Chrysler Championship]]\n|\u221218 (65-69-67-65=266)\n|5 strokes\n|{{flagicon|USA}} [[Tommy Armour III]], {{flagicon|SWE}} [[Jesper Parnevik]]\n|-\n|align=center|25\n|align=right|16 Jan [[2005 PGA Tour|2005]]\n|[[Sony Open in Hawaii]]\n|\u221211 (69-68-67-65=269)\n|1 stroke\n|{{flagicon|ZAF}} [[Ernie Els]]\n|-\n|align=center|26\n|align=right|24 Apr 2005\n|[[Shell Houston Open]] <small>(3)</small>\n|\u221213 (64-71-70-70=275)\n|Playoff\n|{{flagicon|USA}} [[John Daly (golfer)|John Daly]]\n|-\n|align=center|27\n|align=right|8 May 2005\n|[[Wachovia Championship]]\n|\u221212 (70-69-71-66=276)\n|Playoff\n|{{flagicon|USA}} [[Jim Furyk]], {{flagico